                        <description>&lt;p&gt;If you don&apos;t wont to use stemming, StandardAnalyzer miss some french strangeness like elision.&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;l&apos;avion&quot; wich means &quot;the plane&quot; must be tokenized as &quot;avion&quot; (plane).&lt;br/&gt;
This filter could be used with other latin language if elision exists.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
